<div class="text-center mt-4">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560807707-8cc77767d783"
         alt="Rocky"
         class="img-fluid"
         style="width: 500px; height: 500px; object-fit: cover;">
</div>

<div class="container mt-4">
    <p>
        Rocky is a 5-year-old German Shepherd who has overcome incredible odds. Rescued from difficult circumstances, Rocky is now thriving and ready for his forever home.
